Write a Python function to rotate a list by k positions.
AI Response
def rotate(lst, k):
k %= len(lst)
return lst[-k:] + lst[:-k]
print(rotate([1,2,3,4,5], 2)) # [4,5,1,2,3]
Example 4.4
User
Write Python to remove list duplicates preserving order.
AI Response
def unique(lst):
seen = set()
return [x for x in lst if not (x in seen or seen.add(x))]
print(unique([1,2,1,3,2,4])) # [1,2,3,4]
